<br>
If you made a post for every collosal VI fuckup, you'd have yourself a full-time job at that very task.<br>
<br>
On top of that, considering how long PoG, Epics, and even the Drolvarg Captain have been the way they are, the game's overall Risk and Reward is hosed harder than a black man in a 1953 Civil Rights riot. It's beyond repair.<br>
<br>
At this point, the best course of action is to mock them when we can think of something clever, and resort to calling Kendrick (and the other incompetents) a simian with a case of downsydrome so severe that even Corky Thatcher would call him a dumbass.<br>
<br>
That is, until DaoC, SB, AO, Pong 2001, or a new version of Donkey Kong Jr is released.</td></tr></table><br><p>[ No Comments Allowed for Anonymous, please <a href="user.php">register</a>  ]</font><p><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=1519&sid=170&pid=1512&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0#1519">Re: So? LOL</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Monday, April 02 @ 13:48:00 EDT</font><br><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=1520&sid=170&pid=1512&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0#1520">Maybe Verant has better things to think about....</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Monday, April 02 @ 16:39:22 EDT</font><br><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=1521&sid=170&pid=1520&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0#1521">Re: Maybe Verant has better things to think about....</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Monday, April 02 @ 17:52:54 EDT</font><br><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=1522&sid=170&pid=1521&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0#1522">Re: Maybe Verant has better things to think about....</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Monday, April 02 @ 18:30:37 EDT</font><br><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=1528&sid=170&pid=1522&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0#1528">Re: Maybe Verant has better things to think about....</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Monday, April 02 @ 21:12:11 EDT</font><br><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=1529&sid=170&pid=1528&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0#1529">Re: Maybe Verant has better things to think about....</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Monday, April 02 @ 21:51:38 EDT</font><br><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=1533&sid=170&pid=1529&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0#1533">Re: Maybe Verant has better things to think about....</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Monday, April 02 @ 23:47:00 EDT</font><br><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=1546&sid=170&pid=1533&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0#1546">I didn't know...</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Tuesday, April 03 @ 16:23:38 EDT</font><br></ul></ul></ul></ul><li><a hre